.TH POHODA-ZABBIX-DIGEST 1 "May 2026" "pohoda-zabbix 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
pohoda-zabbix-digest \- Pohoda business metrics for Zabbix monitoring
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pohoda-zabbix-digest
[\fIMETRIC\fR]
[\fB\-\-metric\fR=\fIMETRIC\fR]
[\fB\-\-period\fR=\fIPERIOD\fR]
[\fB\-\-env\fR=\fIFILE\fR]
[\fB\-\-debug\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Collects business metrics from Pohoda accounting system via mServer
using shared digest modules. Results are cached per period for 5 minutes.
.PP
When called without arguments, outputs all metrics as JSON for the default
period (last 30 days).
When a metric name is provided, outputs only that metric's value.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-metric=\fIMETRIC\fR, \fIMETRIC\fR
Return a single metric value instead of full JSON.
.TP
.B \-\-period=\fIPERIOD\fR
Time period to analyse. Accepted values:
.RS
.TP
.B month
Last 30 days (default).
.TP
.B year
Current calendar year from January 1st to today.
.TP
.B YYYY
Full calendar year, e.g.\& \fB2024\fR.
.RE
.TP
.B \-\-env=\fIFILE\fR
Path to .env configuration file.
.TP
.B \-\-debug
Pretty-print JSON output.
.SH AVAILABLE METRICS
.SS Debtors
.TP
.B debtors.count
Number of companies with overdue unpaid invoices.
.TP
.B debtors.invoices_count
Total count of overdue unpaid invoices.
.TP
.B debtors.overdue_0_30
Overdue invoices aged 0\(en30 days.
.TP
.B debtors.overdue_31_60
Overdue invoices aged 31\(en60 days.
.TP
.B debtors.overdue_61_90
Overdue invoices aged 61\(en90 days.
.TP
.B debtors.overdue_90plus
Overdue invoices aged more than 90 days.
.SS Outcoming invoices (issued)
.TP
.B outcoming_invoices.count
Total issued invoices in period.
.TP
.B outcoming_invoices.active_count
Non-cancelled issued invoices.
.TP
.B outcoming_invoices.cancelled_count
Cancelled issued invoices.
.SS Incoming invoices (received)
.TP
.B incoming_invoices.count, incoming_invoices.active_count, incoming_invoices.cancelled_count
Counts of received invoices (total / active / cancelled).
.SS Payments
.TP
.B incoming_payments.count
Incoming bank payments in period.
.TP
.B outcoming_payments.count
Outgoing bank payments in period.
.SS Waiting & unmatched
.TP
.B waiting_income.count, waiting_income.total_amount
Unpaid outcoming invoices (count and total amount).
.TP
.B waiting_payments.count, waiting_payments.total_amount
Unpaid incoming invoices (count and total amount).
.TP
.B unmatched_payments.count, unmatched_payments.total_amount
Bank payments not yet matched to an invoice.
.SS Meta
.TP
.B last_run
Unix timestamp of last data collection.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B POHODA_URL
Pohoda mServer URL (e.g.\& http://localhost:5336).
.TP
.B POHODA_USERNAME
mServer username.
.TP
.B POHODA_PASSWORD
mServer password.
.TP
.B POHODA_ICO
Company identification number (IČO).
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
pohoda-zabbix-digest --period=year --debug
Pretty-print all metrics for the current calendar year.
.TP
pohoda-zabbix-digest --period=2024 debtors.count
Return the debtor count for the full year 2024.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR pohoda-zabbix-status (1),
.BR zabbix_agent2 (8)
